                            <comment id="56616" author="cbeams" created="Tue, 10 Aug 2010 13:31:42 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks, Jon.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Documentation now:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Reflects generic use of &lt;tt&gt;ApplicationListener&lt;/tt&gt; interface&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Demonstrates use of &lt;tt&gt;ApplicationEventPublisher(Aware)&lt;/tt&gt; instead of &lt;tt&gt;ApplicationContext(Aware)&lt;/tt&gt; for publishing custom events&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Provides a more complete narrative as to how each of the publisher, listener, and event objects interact with one another&lt;/li&gt;
